name: layers i / radiografía
description:
We all are made up of layers. Feelings, thoughts, external stimuli, conversations we've had, experiences we've lived, hopes, wishes, frustrations, everything.  Layers are made up of elements. The way they are arranged shape us.

If these elements are re-arranged, there's a new us.
If these layers can be read separately, there's a new understanding of us.

This is a series made up of 5 works, representing what we see in our natural state, and other ways of seeing and understanding, plus a 6th work that presents them all together.  Layers i is the first group of 6 works.

Artwork by Marcelo Soria-Rodríguez, @msoriaro. Made with Processing, 3000x6000px.
